01:31:55,619 --> 01:32:00,880
the sky with fantastic colours.

873
01:32:00,880 --> 01:32:05,329
Texas is the second biggest state after Alaska.

874
01:32:05,329 --> 01:32:11,789
There are still cowboys who work there, but
the modern state of Texas, like Alaska, is

875
01:32:11,789 --> 01:32:14,809
rich because of its oil.

876
01:32:14,809 --> 01:32:21,840
The smallest state of the USA is little Rhode
Island to the east of Connecticut.

877
01:32:21,840 --> 01:32:27,730
Newport in Rhode Island has three big music
festivals each year.

878
01:32:27,730 --> 01:32:34,039
In Texas the capital city, Austin, is also
famous for its music.

879
01:32:34,039 --> 01:32:41,500
Janis Joplin sang there, as well as Bruce
Springsteen, Van Morrison, and country singer

880
01:32:41,500 --> 01:32:48,079
Kinky Friedman, who also writes very funny
crime books.

881
01:32:48,079 --> 01:32:55,030
The holiday islands of Hawaii are a long way
from the other states of the USA.

882
01:32:55,030 --> 01:33:02,000
Many Americans go there to enjoy the beaches,
like the famous Waikiki Beach, and the warm

883
01:33:02,000 --> 01:33:03,770
sunshine.

884
01:33:03,770 --> 01:33:09,300
Although there are a lot of tourists, you
can escape to quieter places where you can

885
01:33:09,300 --> 01:33:16,090
see trees, waterfalls and many unusual plants
and birds.

886
01:33:16,090 --> 01:33:22,480
There are sadly only 9,000 true Hawaiians,
but around a third of the people who live

887
01:33:22,480 --> 01:33:26,690
in the islands are part-Hawaiian.

888
01:33:26,690 --> 01:33:33,059
But there are more interesting and exciting
places to visit in the USA than will fit into

889
01:33:33,059 --> 01:33:34,860
one book.

890
01:33:34,860 --> 01:33:44,760
Choose what you prefer, busy city or quiet
national park, cold mountains or warm sea,

891
01:33:44,760 --> 01:34:02,570
shopping or sports, and plan your own American
journey!

892
01:34:02,570 --> 01:34:05,530
- THE END -

